Skeem Saam actor Masilo Magoro is on the radar of the repo men for failing to hand over his BMW. If the bank gets its way, the popular actor, who plays the controversial character of Charles Kunutu on the SABC1 youth drama, will have to join the queues at the Bree taxi rank for his travels from next week. This comes after BMW Financial Services obtained a default judgment against the actor at the South Gauteng High Court against his bad debt. TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE